p.e:
I AVOID McDERMOT'S TAVERN.
LAST WEEK I STOPPED IN FOR A
PINT, AND AS RUDE AS IT WAS
THE ENTIRE ESTABLISHMENT JUST
STOPPED TALKING AT ONCE.

A FEW PEOPLE IN ROBES GOT UP
AND LEFT ENTIRELY.

OTHERS I KEPT CATCHING LOOKING
AT ME.

IT MIGHT SOUND ASANINE BUT I
SUSPECT THERE'S A TOWN SECRET
BEING KEPT FROM ME...

I ENDEAVOR TO DISCOVER IT.

--A.W.
